# Backend Service Conventions

See [MASTER_BLUEPRINT.md](../../MASTER_BLUEPRINT.md) for full implementations.

- ESM modules (`"type": "module"`), Fastify 4.x, Pino logger
- Shared Prisma schema at repo root `prisma/schema.prisma`
- JWT via `@fastify/jwt`; auth middleware in `middleware/authenticate.js`
- Validate request bodies with Zod before processing
- Rate limiting via `@fastify/rate-limit`
- Split routes into `routes/*.routes.js`, keep `server.js` as bootstrap only
